                className: "english",
                children: "It does happen more often that medicines naturally have a certain price and that only comes about when the negotiators have agreed on a price and until that time you have to wait. So that's really very annoying for some cases. So we do have patients who say, when is it now? I read on the internet that it's approved. Yes, but the reimbursement isn't arranged yet. Yes."
