                className: "english",
                children: "But I'm not dissatisfied, because you also have to learn enormously much yourself as lab captain, as every role within a team. But I also couldn't have expected that I would do all the things you have to do... Besides that of course, I spent a lot of work on the podcast, so you have to do that on the side. I've been entrepreneurship captain within a team the whole time. Someone else does that now, but I still help with that too. So it's not that I'm only in the lab from 9 to 5 every day. I'm just busy with a hundred thousand other things, just like everyone within a team. And that also makes it more difficult to just think, okay, this is coming up in the lab, so we have to make this and that."
